Interface Deployment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Refreshable<Deployment>, Updatable<Deployment.Update>, Wrapper<DeploymentExtendedInner>

    public interface Deployment
extends Refreshable<Deployment>, Updatable<Deployment.Update>, Wrapper<DeploymentExtendedInner>
    An immutable client-side representation of an Azure deployment.
